package Commands
Commands used to create command line.

    Description

    Base command of tree Add.
    IAddDepartmentCommand
    Command to add departments.
    IAddStudentCommand

    Root CLI command.
    ICheckSummerCommand
    Command to calculate and output checkSum - Exclusive disjunction on all bytes of file.

    IFirstLongestCommand
    Command to find the longest row in a file.

    IRemoveStudentCommand

    IShowDepartmentCommand

    IShowInstituteCommand

    IShowStudentCommand
    Command which shows student as instructed.
    IStudentsCounterCommand
    This command tells how many students are there in institue as instructed.
    IStudentsFilterCommand
    This command filters students as instructed.
